      <title>所罗门群岛任命前外长马内莱为中国领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/solomon-islands-elects-ex-foreign-minister-manele-as-new-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[所罗门群岛外交部长耶利米·马内莱已获得立法者的支持，成为该国新总理，即使在亲北京领导人索加瓦雷离开后，也加强了中国在这个太平洋国家的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/solomon-islands-elects-ex-foreign-minister-manele-as-new-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 01:18:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登现在称盟友日本与中国、俄罗斯一样“仇外”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/biden-now-calls-ally-japan-xenophobic-along-with-china-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登在华盛顿举行的竞选筹款活动上发表讲话时，将盟友日本以及竞争对手中国和俄罗斯列入他所谓的“仇外”国家名单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/biden-now-calls-ally-japan-xenophobic-along-with-china-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 01:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁卢特尼克和保尔森将在纽约为特朗普举办筹款活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/billionaires-lutnick-paulson-to-host-fundraiser-for-trump-in-ny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁霍华德·卢特尼克、约翰·保尔森和伍迪·约翰逊等富有捐助者将于本月晚些时候在曼哈顿为唐纳德·特朗普举办筹款活动，这位共和党候选人希望筹集 2024 年的战争资金，而刑事审判限制了他的竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/billionaires-lutnick-paulson-to-host-fundraiser-for-trump-in-ny</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 23:25:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国地方选举投票可能考验苏纳克的领导力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/uk-votes-in-local-elections-that-may-test-sunak-s-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国人将于周四进行一系列地方选举，如果执政的保守党遭受重大损失，英国首相里希·苏纳克可能会陷入危险境地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/uk-votes-in-local-elections-that-may-test-sunak-s-leadership</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉马杜罗在投票前将最低工资提高至 130 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/venezuela-s-maduro-increases-minimum-wage-to-130-ahead-of-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉将把工人的月收入增加 30%，尼古拉斯·马杜罗 (Nicolás Maduro) 寻求在 7 月总统选举前加强支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/venezuela-s-maduro-increases-minimum-wage-to-130-ahead-of-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 22:39:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
